BK_SUPER_SALES_CHANNEL_CODE = NSSCT. BK_SUPER_SALES_CHANNEL_CODE AND NSSCT.END_TV_DATE = DATE '3500-01-01') WHERE SOLD_TO.TRANSACTION_SOURCE_CD = 'ERP'
UNION ALL
